{"tid":95440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美MVP級女將加盟中藍賽,不敵毒霧僅17小時就回國","createTime":"2017-01-26T04:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T09:10:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b4a2eb27eece68b0334759442ec2c3101d2055","tid":95440,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/uK5XOB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FuK5XOB.jpg&h=e1ff196b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Za6uW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FZa6uW3.jpg&h=d3542b34&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017/01/26 08:02 <br />\n<br />\n〔體育中心／綜合報導〕山西竹葉青女籃原要請曾拿過WNBA年度最佳球員的多恩（Elena Delle Donne）助陣，未料多恩不適應當地的「空氣」，並指自己有「萊姆病」，抵達中國山西太原後僅17小時就回美國。 <br />\n<br />\n多恩是在24日抵達太原，當時在機場有許多中國球迷來接機，但不到一天的時間，多恩就決定要返回美國。 <br />\n<br />\n籃球評論員侯向鋒在微博上說，「山西竹葉青女籃超級外援在降落到太原17個小時的加盟新聞發布會變成了通氣會&mdash;&mdash;多恩由於不能適應這裡的空氣情況，由於本身患有『萊姆病』，引發身體不適，決定即刻返回美國，不再為山西征戰。」 <br />\n<br />\n中國山西霧霾嚴重，其中臨汾市二氧化硫濃度居高不下，中國科學院氣象學博士後李汀曾說，這種含有高濃度二氧化硫的毒霧稱為「酸霧」，吸入恐引起急性肺水腫甚至死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n多恩上賽季在芝加哥天空效力，繳出平均21.5分、7.0個籃板，她曾在2015年賽季拿下年度MVP、得分王，她也代表美國女籃在2016年里約奧運中奪得金牌。"},{"pid":"1736e65fb7ec6e0f9da92dcc55a1e2df61b5b9d3","tid":95440,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"MAYA MOORE唔係壟斷左WNBA MVP女1多年咩?"},{"pid":"2f1dd426c846ddf2022012a0b22c613261be86ff","tid":95440,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"籃同藍<br />\n唔識分？"},{"pid":"518d4c4734a243b6f751eb76ba71aee8c7491112","tid":95440,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"中國人慢慢吸啦<br />\n<br />\n鬼妹梗係即走啦"},{"pid":"01b413d9ed712edfa2a344b95869d4413f42bfc0","tid":95440,"uid":63187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"鬼妹呢d 數據應該仲可以係wnba屈機嫁wor<br />\n仲洗乜走去中國"},{"pid":"59138faf00ae293198462c43931d7caa88508c66","tid":95440,"uid":9610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼妹呢d 數據應該仲可以係wnba屈機嫁wor<br />\n仲洗乜走去中國</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwnba啲球員好多都會休季嗰陣去外國打波<br />\n唔同nba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0a3340b34ce0cb6633c5e6bec5e46eb9e76643","tid":95440,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"落機望下個天就知咩事<br />\n唔走=自殺"},{"pid":"da4c02f980bee3fd7c5ed431fd227f178f992118","tid":95440,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"好想比佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c6433352c9f1bbd54ad539e1175c1641ed6d2e","tid":95440,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae465191fffe89d03a93c81832fb441473b0f4fe","tid":95440,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"美帝又係度說三道四發放祖國不利傳聞<br />\n我絕不會讓他們狼子野心得逞"},{"pid":"623b5ff0019a5a514077dade2792aa39b83556ef","tid":95440,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>籃同藍<br />\n唔識分？</blockquote><br />\n算啦，華文媒體不嬲都求鳩其其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好旨意華媒有職業操守"},{"pid":"58e7262a116e298bed57ac484a7afa2dda67ceae","tid":95440,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"華人賤種地區就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fc2a6e8a89f7e2adc39bf4ce572b2ac8c23299","tid":95440,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\